{"tid":533571,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"是誰偷走了C朗的時間？","createTime":"2018-01-19T02:08:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T07:39:06.000Z","uid":28758,"like":11,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e12c7694424cbb54de31751afb515bea026b10cc","tid":533571,"uid":28758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T02:08:35.000Z","msg":"西甲聯賽,頂多都只係六個月 <br />\n但係C朗過去一年的時間? <br />\n到底去左邊? <br />\n點解大家好似一點印象都無 <br />\n記憶比篡改了?還是時間被盜走了 <br />\n是神偷了?是美斯偷了?還是C朗自己偷了 <br />\n我通通都不知道,但我只知道,那段時間是C朗的寶貴回憶 <br />\n<br />\n衛冕歐聯,一個西甲,一個國際足總最佳球員獎,一個歐聯最佳球員<br />\n它們到底去了邊? <br />\n點解大家只把重點收在C朗在聯賽既小小失敗 <br />\n而忘記了它們? <br />\n話C朗獨食,唔該你自己睇下皇馬精華,睇下C朗助攻數<br />\n話C朗唔識射罰球,自己睇下西甲罰球數據 <br />\n話C朗黑面,自己睇下C朗平時接受待人接物,有幾好笑容 <br />\n皇馬好多隊友都話C朗最好相處 更衣室入邊最無架子 <br />\n<br />\n你估C朗踢皇馬既時候<br />\n唔想有好似足球小將咁既知心隊友 <br />\n唔想有好似ONE PIECE咁既團結志同道合的夥伴 <br />\n無啊,佢只係一個愛德華艾力克 <br />\n手腳受傷了,要獨自背負罪名去尋找入球 <br />\n<br />\n點解短短一兩個月 <br />\n一向團結既連登會變到分裂 <br />\n大家平時反美斯既精神 <br />\n點解會盪然無存? <br />\n大家可以回來嗎"},{"pid":"4ffe7c91c7bcdcbb13091690d96f4cc9707471e8","tid":533571,"uid":70988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T02:25:06.000Z","msg":"連登幾時有團結過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81fdf262a0c07752069678b5edcaf8d16e24672","tid":533571,"uid":106933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T02:30:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>皇馬好多隊友都話C朗最好相處 更衣室入邊最無架子</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊個隊友夠膽話佢有架子呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde03fa712f78609fee938402c4692af972f2f18","tid":533571,"uid":24387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T02:31:16.000Z","msg":"連登仔一直都on99架啦 風吹邊面去邊面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa5abe947f68229de399851cd010890e7a4c8c7","tid":533571,"uid":34158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T04:33:12.000Z","msg":"john gor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c86edebaeaa2c9a05657d580331faf1f41c1257","tid":533571,"uid":28758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T05:52:26.000Z","msg":"剩係識比負評"},{"pid":"258a923ec244797a40ae92d0fb68a2e374f3a33d","tid":533571,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaa5abe947f68229de399851cd010890e7a4c8c7","tid":533571,"uid":34158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T04:33:12.000Z","msg":"john gor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"239ee9cec718f4032062d56fe1f2a7e388415fd7","tid":533571,"uid":33601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:31:21.000Z","msg":"牙朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/163120_024d51eceba9d84a40269d68b77b1e85.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F163120_024d51eceba9d84a40269d68b77b1e85.gif&h=bdffda48&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80396c9a2796c42d80e19f1fa4d6430f6983c5d5","tid":533571,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:40:06.000Z","msg":"英超聯賽,頂多都只係六個月 <br />\n但係巴禾過去一年的時間? <br />\n到底去左邊? <br />\n點解大家好似一點印象都無 <br />\n記憶比篡改了?還是時間被盜走了 <br />\n是哥帥偷了?是艾達臣偷了?還是巴禾自己偷了 <br />\n我通通都不知道,但我只知道,那段時間是巴禾的寶貴回憶"},{"pid":"1a790dd3c154fb938e523ca30fea58bcc8fad4d0","tid":533571,"uid":101464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:50:26.000Z","msg":"John John <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe3fc6cc747d20b4916